#Makeup101 Green Eye Makeup Look

Ever wonder what's the best eye makeup colour for Indian skin tones? The answer is green. Green hues instantly enhance dusky complexion without making it look unnatural. Want to learn? Nikita (@nikitabhattmakeup )shows you how to ace the green-tone look. 

#Makeup101 #makeup #glam #glammakeup #greeneyemakeup #makeuptutorial #beginnermakeup #learnmakeup #beauty #beautytips #tutorial #beautymakeup #smoothmakeup #feminaindia

Focus on creating a fake crease just above the natural fold of your eyelid while working on hooded eyes. This way the colour won’t get lost while the eyes are open. ✨
